video.title: The Circle
video.synopsis: Status and strategy collide in this social experiment and competition show where online players flirt, befriend and catfish their way toward $100,000.

episodes.synopsis: Ready for first impressions? The experiment begins as the players craft their profiles and start connecting ... for better or worse.
episodes.title: Hello, Circle

episodes.synopsis: A surprise confrontation raises the stakes of the game. Later, the players get ready to party, and a special guest scopes out the competition.
episodes.title: Face-to-Face

episodes.synopsis: An anonymous game of “Ask Me Anything” leads to a series of accusations. Meanwhile, Miranda refines her cheeky strategy, and Shubham finds his voice.
episodes.title: There's a Catfish Among Us

episodes.synopsis: Another tense elimination leads to an honest conversation, a casual connection evolves into an intimate bond, and a quirky new player joins the game.
episodes.title: Planting Doubt

episodes.synopsis: As a new day dawns, a fresh face joins the Circle -- and presents a series of stirring questions. Rebecca turns the heat up on the gameplay.
episodes.title: Sliding into DMs

episodes.synopsis: Mercedeze faces her toughest critics and makes a candid request. Two new influencers are picked, and one player must say goodbye.
episodes.title: Anonymous Trolling

episodes.synopsis: Two new players settle into the Circle, just in time for trivia night. On the heels of a competitive match, Sammie makes an emotional reveal.
episodes.title: Picking Teams

episodes.synopsis: Tension and tenderness intersect as the influencers deal with an elimination twist, and two players connect in person. A new face joins the fun.
episodes.title: The Player I'm Saving Is ...

episodes.synopsis: How about another round of shake-ups? Sean shares a personal secret with the Circle, and a face-to-face meeting makes for an unusual bond.
episodes.title: Instant Block

episodes.synopsis: The Circle dials up the drama with a cutthroat round of true confessions. The game’s first “superinfluencer” steps into power.
episodes.title: Declare Your Rival

episodes.synopsis: As the experiment winds down, Sammie and Ed bond over similar suspicions. The players prepare to choose a winner -- and orchestrate one last block.
episodes.title: The Last Rating

episodes.synopsis: The truth finally comes to light when the finalists meet in the flesh, and at the players reunion, the winner is announced.
episodes.title: Finale

episodes.synopsis: The game begins as eight players — including a familiar face from “Too Hot to Handle” — move in, make profiles and (warily) mingle.
episodes.title: Back and More Savage Than Ever

episodes.synopsis: As the influencers consider their pivotal picks, the others continue building relationships. Also, creativity and cringe collide during a poetry slam.
episodes.title: Alliances Are Formed

episodes.synopsis: A new player sparks excitement and uncertainty. Savannah spills the tea — and targets a former ally. A game of Truth or Dare takes a tense turn.
episodes.title: Bye, Bye, Bye!

episodes.synopsis: Bad blood continues to boil between Terilisha and Savannah, leaving the other players torn about their loyalties. Chloe questions Emily’s game play.
episodes.title: Lines Are Drawn

episodes.synopsis: As Courtney takes control of an intriguing twist, the others reconvene and unpack some elimination drama. Meanwhile, two new players join the game.
episodes.title: Snake in the Grass

episodes.synopsis: A new day dawns as Chloe considers her feelings for Trevor — and Mitchell. The Joker shakes up the ranking. Terilisha and Khat explore a new theory.
episodes.title: A Love Triangle

episodes.synopsis: A blocked player pays a visit and plants new seeds of skepticism. Khat puts Lance’s identity to the test. Jonathan Van Ness pops in for a challenge.
episodes.title: Friend Zoned....

episodes.synopsis: Tensions mount as catfish accusations fly. Meanwhile, an anonymous round of Q&A stirs the pot, and a unique double block redefines the game.
episodes.title: Damage Control

episodes.synopsis: Khat takes aim at Chloe’s integrity — much to the dismay of her allies. Trevor pursues a better bond with Mitchell. A new player makes himself at home.
episodes.title: A New Twist

episodes.synopsis: The sweet sound of patriotism sweeps through the Circle as the players take part in Democracy Day. An elimination deliberation gets personal.
episodes.title: Campaigning to Win

episodes.synopsis: After a major blocking, the players decode a departing message. Two competing duos craft new plans. The Circle goes glam for an awards ceremony.
episodes.title: The Master Plan

episodes.synopsis: The players brace for a final blocking and attempt to build last-minute bonds. Chloe faces a hard truth. The Circle reveals a new influencer twist.
episodes.title: The Last Blocking

episodes.synopsis: Host Michelle Buteau greets the finalists as they prepare for one last rating — and a face-to-face meetup. Who will take home the $100,000 prize?
episodes.title: And the Winner Is...

episodes.synopsis: The game begins as the players make profiles and share their interests, including shirtless selfies, family bickering and a casual blocking.
episodes.title: Circle, Did You Miss Me?

episodes.synopsis: A shocking shake-up leaves the players divided — and more confused than ever. Meanwhile, one jokester initiates a group chat with like-minded friends.
episodes.title: A New Twist

episodes.synopsis: After a pivotal vote, the group grapples with a wave of skepticism. Two new players join the Circle. A flashback photo game reveals new truths.
episodes.title: Identity Theft

episodes.synopsis: A morning chat sparks fresh flirtation, the players throw shade during an anonymous review session, and the influencers receive a last-minute alert.
episodes.title: A Flirtatious Alliance

episodes.synopsis: After a face-to-face blocking, a competitor stirs the pot. The Wolf Pack grows as a new alliance takes shape. Lil Yachty stops by for a rap battle.
episodes.title: The Real Michelle

episodes.synopsis: An enthusiastic newbie joins the game and catches up on lingering drama. Elsewhere, the group prepares for a rating that's chock-full of surprises.
episodes.title: A New Member of the Wolfpack

episodes.synopsis: Tension leads to tenderness as a blocked player bids farewell, but not before gifting a secret advantage. A mysterious ghost hunter joins the game.
episodes.title: Shock Blocking

episodes.synopsis: Things take a sweet — and strategic — turn as the players decorate cakes. Later, one ally tests another's loyalty, and two new influencers take control.
episodes.title: Full Out War

episodes.synopsis: A double-blocking bombshell leaves the players speechless. A sudden alert sheds new light on a secret reality, and an avid gamer gets ready to play.
episodes.title: Ghostbusting & Catfishing

episodes.synopsis: A player speaks the truth — and puts a target on another’s back. An alert triggers a sigh of relief, and a group chat showdown gets personal.
episodes.title: A Circle Divided

episodes.synopsis: After a bit of back and forth, the influencers agree on a block. A departing player spills some tea. Plus, the Circle goes glam for prom night!
episodes.title: Choosing Sides

episodes.synopsis: The final blocking draws closer, but not before a suite of emotional messages arrive. Also, the players start to sweat during a savage round of Q&A.
episodes.title: The Final Stretch

episodes.synopsis: Michelle Buteau delivers surprise and delight as the final five reflect on their gameplay and get ready for the grand reveal of this season’s winner.
episodes.title: Finale
